)Attr
 $ type(input) caps(off) hilite(uscore) intens(low)
 _ type(input) caps(on ) hilite(uscore) intens(low)
 @ type(output) caps(off)
)Body Window(57,13)
+
+Command ===>$zcmd
+
+Your%.ssh+directory allows write permissions to those  +
+in your group and universal which is%not+allowed.      +
+
+Change%.ssh+permissions to%700+to fix this:_z+(Y)
+
+Press%Enter+to Change, or%F3+to Cancel.
+
+Current Directory:@file
+Current Permissions:@perms
+
)Init
 &zwinttl = 'ZIGI .ssh Permissions Alert'
 .zvars = '(zigiperm)'
 .help = zigihprm
)Proc
 ver (&zigiperm,list,Y)
)END
